{"tid":384781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咩係愛情 結婚又係為咩","createTime":"2017-09-02T15:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T12:52:47.000Z","uid":143065,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"131cceae249cb8f5c41b2e579c8178b7e9e64fc1","tid":384781,"uid":143065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"過往有幾段感情經歷<br />\n令自己唔再完全訓身於愛情<br />\n<br />\n見到身邊朋友<br />\n嗰個付出所有 all in 去愛 迎合男朋友<br />\n自問一定唔會<br />\n即使對身邊人都會有保留<br />\n無論屋企人定男朋友<br />\n<br />\n我曾經被男朋友傷害過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家都原諒左佢 但都會有條刺<br />\n令自己唔再all in <br />\n即使依家男朋友都好似對我好好<br />\n但總會有所懷疑<br />\n已經冇能力再完全相信佢<br />\n大家都一齊左一段長時間<br />\n都向住結婚條路行<br />\n只係 我仍然抱有懷疑<br />\n覺得始終睇唔清佢個人 個心諗緊咩<br />\n<br />\n好可悲 <br />\n究竟世界上仲有冇真愛<br />\n點解要結婚？<br />\n結婚係真係兩個完全信任, 愛對方的人結合<br />\n定只係時間同條件都match <br />\n你對佢都有d愛 唔抗拒 佢對你好<br />\n就決定行埋落去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n愛對方 完全all in 完全信任對方<br />\n真係好勇敢<br />\n<br />\n直到依家仍然對身邊人 唔會完全信任<br />\n我係個可憐人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4afafd4f150ed6fa8dc9fcdd0e333c61954fae","tid":384781,"uid":136252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:15:40.000Z","msg":"想有個伴"},{"pid":"711d42b1abf4f8874b13d4afc16e3003a28f4e99","tid":384781,"uid":90523,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"個心有條刺咁仲點行落去，你原諒左佢，但你信唔到佢，其實結果都會分手<br />\n利申:過來人"},{"pid":"5e93cab194b1fa8a1db0b3f5413c405798b31a87","tid":384781,"uid":143065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個心有條刺咁仲點行落去，你原諒左佢，但你信唔到佢，其實結果都會分手<br />\n利申:過來人</blockquote><br />\n自問年紀都唔細<br />\n身邊親戚朋友都睇好我哋會結婚<br />\n（佢地唔知嗰件事）<br />\n同我都算門當戶對 條件match <br />\n佢依家都對我好好<br />\n<br />\n即使有時候仍然會諗起<br />\n又怕自己年紀慢慢大<br />\n搵唔到一個好似佢條件ok對我好的人<br />\n<br />\n所以之前麥明詩之前關於女人慢慢貶值嘅說話<br />\n其實我都好同意<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span><br />\n<br />\nSad but very true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf033abf0f40032850ea606a916f9d0980725c0","tid":384781,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"結婚係女人年紀開始大搵唔到更好既選擇"},{"pid":"bc084a54bae0984feec7782379d5ef372a6e51d9","tid":384781,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"到最後宜家有無同佢分手定仲一齊緊？"},{"pid":"ceec38fbdee91686d12c07f459ded593e8bc4146","tid":384781,"uid":143065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到最後宜家有無同佢分手定仲一齊緊？</blockquote><br />\n依家仲一齊緊<br />\n<br />\n身邊親戚朋友個個覺得佢好仔 條件好<br />\n有人甚至話過 覺得我襯唔起佢<br />\n真係有苦自己知<br />\n但冇理由周圍同人講佢曾經對唔住我<br />\n........<br />\n其實係咪只係我太在意身邊嘅人嘅諗法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我唔係同呢個結婚<br />\n我肯定兩老都會失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e87537df2387e8f0ba414f813606adbd63330f6","tid":384781,"uid":73761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"中出"},{"pid":"97eab19a8d821f78631d2487a32e344472beaaf7","tid":384781,"uid":121349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply